export%20orig%3D%22chr2_34_22%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2234%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Hilkiah%20and%20the%20other%20men%20went%20to%20the%20New%20Quarter%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E34%3A22a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Second%20Quarter%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20newer%20section%20of%20Jerusalem.%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Mishneh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Jerusalem%20to%20consult%20with%20the%20prophet%20Huldah.%20She%20was%20the%20wife%20of%20Shallum%20son%20of%20Tikvah%2C%20son%20of%20Harhas%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E34%3A22b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20parallel%20text%20at%202%26%23xA0%3BKgs%2022%3A14%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Eson%20of%20Tokhath%2C%20son%20of%20Hasrah.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20keeper%20of%20the%20Temple%20wardrobe.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_34_23%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2234%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EShe%20said%20to%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20has%20spoken!%20Go%20back%20and%20tell%20the%20man%20who%20sent%20you%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_34_24%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%2234%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20I%20am%20going%20to%20bring%20disaster%20on%20this%20city%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E34%3A24%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethis%20place%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2034%3A27%2C%2028.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20its%20people.%20All%20the%20curses%20written%20in%20the%20